-- French Payroll Cost Cuts Will Create Jobs, Bertrand says on RTL
-- B y   A d r i a   C i m i n o
-- 2012-01-31T07:12:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-31/french-payroll-cost-cuts-will-create-jobs-bertrand-says-on-rtl.html
Cuts in payroll costs paid by
employers will  create jobs  and increase competitiveness, Labor
Minister Xavier Bertrand said on RTL radio.  “Each time you lower costs, it favors employment,”
Bertrand said in the interview. He didn’t say how many jobs the
measure would create.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adria Cimino in Paris at 
